Name: Multi-Scoop Ice Cream
AttributesDescription: Reduces Flight STA consumption for all Resonators in the team by 18% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: With a makeshift mini ice cream maker, Roccia serves up simple ice cream that's both generous in portion and light on the pocket. It's become a beloved treat among the troupe, satisfying their cravings for sweets without straining their budget.
